Report of girls who are approached to make false claims against Deputy Minister Mduduzi Manana spread on social media.Manana appeared in Randburg magistrates court for allegedly assaulting a woman in Cubana night club. His appearance in Randburg magistrates court come just days after he issued an apology to the woman he allegedly assaulted. I know that my actions and those of the people in my company have disappointed and hurt many people in the country. As a leader I should have known better and acted better. I will subject myself fully to the process of the law and give it my full co-operation Manana said.A tweet by someone by the name of Nosipho Ngema is making rounds on Twitter where the person claims that her friends were approached to make false accusation against Manana.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; comments